{"tid":2423823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國將公布財政預算案  料大量派糖 減稅谷經濟","createTime":"2021-02-26T06:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T12:33:10.000Z","uid":227801,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"deaa67f6638f1ee769f0abb6f165483236cd4954","tid":2423823,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:57:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">講個笑話 ：二等公民</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國財相辛偉誠（Rishi Sunak）將於下周三（3月3日）公布新一份財政預算案，據多間外媒報導，辛偉誠將會「派糖」並推出多項刺激經濟措施，包括大派消費劵、寬減食肆及酒吧的酒稅，協助英國經濟在解除封城措施後加快反彈。<br />\n英國官員：夏天或不再強制戴口罩&nbsp;【下一頁】<br />\n辛偉誠將於下周三公布新一份財政預算案，預料採取一系統措施幫助陷入困境的行業及鼓勵國民外出消費。據《每日郵報》 指，財政部官員正研究更多措施刺激英國經濟復甦，包括提供消費劵鼓勵國民外出購物、降低食肆及酒吧的酒稅、以及逐步把減稅措施推展至超級市場出售的酒精飲品。<br />\n<br />\n此外，辛偉誠亦會考慮重推名為「Eat Out to Help Out」的資助外出用膳計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經濟日報, 非黃營：<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2886440/%E8%8B%B1%E8%B2%A1%E7%9B%B8%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%91%E9%87%91%E9%8C%A2%20%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E6%96%99%E6%B4%BE%E7%B3%96%E6%B8%9B%E7%A8%85%E8%B0%B7%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2886440%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%2591%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%258C%25A2%2520%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%25B3%2596%25E6%25B8%259B%25E7%25A8%2585%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd64lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=fe659a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2886440/%E8%8B%B1%E8%B2%A1%E7%9B%B8%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%91%E9%87%91%E9%8C%A2%20%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E6%96%99%E6%B4%BE%E7%B3%96%E6%B8%9B%E7%A8%85%E8%B0%B7%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F?mtc=20023</a>"},{"pid":"fa6f40d110cd04ac472c0df7573ac4421d805dd0","tid":2423823,"uid":8308,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10